{"tid":2346465,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「惡」夢再起！SONY宣布重啟版《惡靈古堡》電影殺青並預定明年上映！","createTime":"2020-12-30T09:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T11:43:41.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a574d3d73db8e71e477d01aa51f32da1ffc4c7c","tid":2346465,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.toy-people.com/?p=58522&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D58522%26&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSKZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=091eb9a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.toy-people.com/?p=58522&amp;</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/160924549728.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F160924549728.jpg&h=5dab7e6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宣稱以「回歸遊戲原點」為噱頭的生存恐怖電玩《惡靈古堡》( Biohazard / Resident-Evil )重啟版電影，今天 SONY 影業總算是在推特上公布導演導演約翰尼斯羅勃茲( Johannes Roberts )的原話：「浣熊市相關作業已經完成( That's a wrap in Raccoon City. )」暗示電影殺青。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/160924645343.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F160924645343.jpg&h=cde045c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於導演之前就已經強調過是以電玩版《惡靈古堡》一二代的劇情為架構改編，因此大家熟悉的克里斯與克雷兒兄妹，還有吉兒與那位「薪水太多」的里昂都會在故事中登場，同時也會稍加帶到保護傘企業( Umbrella Corp.)的幕後老闆：奧斯華E史賓瑟(Ozwell E Spencer)博士的冰山一角..<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/160924675235.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F160924675235.jpg&h=f7b29843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(射擊遊戲《惡靈古堡：黑暗編年史》中出現的史賓瑟...)<br />\n<br />\n目前《惡靈古堡》除了由 SONY 進行電影重啟之外，另外 Netflix 也在著手進行影集化，大家也別忘了遊戲最新作《惡靈古堡 8 》也即將於 2021 年推出，電影也預計於 2021 年上映。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖片來源：CAPCOM、SONY官方推特)"},{"pid":"9db95835dda5f6023a0aad60b296eabe1d91a82e","tid":2346465,"uid":4574,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"Wuhan city?"},{"pid":"cea180d57c6b947e498711318961da571f739ce8","tid":2346465,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0da242a36ac56e0e4d20c07ec4329ac74fb5907","tid":2346465,"uid":278082,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:04:44.000Z","msg":"美娜都拍左咁多集<br />\n<br />\n宜家先呢跟原著，仲有乜新鮮感？？？"},{"pid":"d0893f1b3f50b02387ec99ebee20678a589ebdc0","tid":2346465,"uid":324041,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"真人阿Jill咁醜樣，罷睇!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab2de2da64462d150d5a4c878a04dba7661124e","tid":2346465,"uid":34523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:20:01.000Z","msg":"如果有大宅大堂鏡頭同Jill sandwich一定入場"},{"pid":"01cc20cd174235484cbe425536e9aebb6ba0d032","tid":2346465,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ab2de2da64462d150d5a4c878a04dba7661124e","tid":2346465,"uid":34523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:20:01.000Z","msg":"如果有大宅大堂鏡頭同Jill sandwich一定入場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"Jill sandwich ，經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d299f86012eb66c5aad1db1e7dc786cc74e183c","tid":2346465,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a943658ec38f902e1d724b2ae1ea35801af001","tid":2346465,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:43:41.000Z","msg":"終於放棄左超能力alice電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/